		<div class="card-body">
			<h2 id="global-rules">Global Rules</h2><p>These are the global rules for our network. Please make sure you read over them before you begin your adventure!</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"><a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/17CRaGNyy0ra9Gzk50lLEJBvynRc6H3oxHBxmVv8HARs/edit?usp&#x3D;sharing"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">Vortex Network | Global Rules</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">Global Rules Last updated November 5th, 2021 Please review the rules for the planet you are playing as well as the following. Disclaimers Joking or pretending to break a rule may result in the same punishment as breaking the rule itself. It is not the staff’s job to determine whether or not...</div><div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/docs/documents/images/kix-favicon7.ico" alt=""><span class="kg-bookmark-author">Google Docs</span></div></div><div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ZmDXkWlVR19PffavBnGCg6A6DEcG5uKk7QMq2UcsHIz0T-C5z0exTHC3gtkATwEAuxQjACKF-xGjNA&#x3D;w1200-h630-p" alt=""></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id="prison-plasma-rules">Prison Plasma Rules</h2><p>These are the planet rules for Prison Plasma. Please make sure you read over them before you begin your adventure!</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"><a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TRKQ7MjDTdW8YU3nQfVvaNMZvF2COna3bD5Hzuwio0U/edit?usp&#x3D;sharing"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">Vortex Network | Prison Plasma Rules</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">Prison Plasma Rules Last updated December 22nd, 2021 Please review the global rules as well as the following DISCLAIMERS Players caught repeatedly breaking rules will be given a significantly harsher punishment. Players caught repeatedly attempting to break rules by pushing limits will be p...</div><div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/docs/documents/images/kix-favicon7.ico" alt=""><span class="kg-bookmark-author">Google Docs</span></div></div><div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/XdQIXS1NRvqxpCVyfMA2Gl60pbC4SdYBpd4ZAUTcwOf595iIgpDHhGk-vE5W3dzE7NUvArPRzoJr0w&#x3D;w1200-h630-p" alt=""></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id="skybock-pandora-rules">Skybock Pandora Rules</h2><p>These are the planet rules for Skyblock Pandora. Please make sure you read over them before you begin your adventure!</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"><a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1m-UqZOAwyr4vGnjwBTO_wfVPMARfZKr2Az9Vk4xOsF0/edit"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">Vortex Network | Skyblock Pandora Rules</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">Disclaimers These rules may be entitled to change throughout the map, stay updated through the changelog channel on the Vortex Discord Rules have multiple punishments given when broken (Refer to Global Rules) Only the Skyblock Administrators and the Skyblock Coordinator have the final say and may...</div><div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/docs/documents/images/kix-favicon7.ico" alt=""><span class="kg-bookmark-author">Google Docs</span></div></div><div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/dkuXB101UChcELtVGZaVKWPD0kPcArvRwc7XR3rYamRirAuJePrOsWcHNr0LWjckIU77PVCSNMywDQ&#x3D;w1200-h630-p" alt=""></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id="survival-earth-rules">Survival Earth Rules</h2><p>These are the planet rules for Survival Earth. Please make sure you read over them before you begin your adventure!</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"><a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RGyPm1NJY23MwSaLKclubIMbJRK6gLbqILIp9szG3tY/edit?usp&#x3D;sharing"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">Vortex Network | Survival Earth Rules</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">Survival Earth Rules Last updated January 8th, 2022 Please review the global rules as well as the following DISCLAIMERS Players caught repeatedly breaking rules will be given a significantly harsher punishment. Players caught repeatedly attempting to break rules by pushing limits will be pu...</div><div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/docs/documents/images/kix-favicon7.ico" alt=""><span class="kg-bookmark-author">Google Docs</span></div></div><div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/S31ssx5fid0R0tmjsIDTPHiqNWocO79GHPFqa5Gae2dRegTzxJhSCSlLV5TyKhp1MI4av4DMtPMH6g&#x3D;w1200-h630-p" alt=""></div></a></figure>
